{"tid":1289597,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"市民成本最細的抗爭方式","createTime":"2019-07-06T07:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T14:36:50.000Z","uid":274862,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e43b4e366a0dba658aa41d88a65491899e85b1d4","tid":1289597,"uid":274862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"之前遊行都有成果, 但要大家放假時, 人多才有力量, 機動性也不夠。遊行的人也未必次次出來。<br />\n<br />\n我們或可推一推成本更細的抗爭方式 - 黑衫日<br />\n<br />\n例如星期五, 全港個個就穿黑衫, 不影響自己本來的工作, 收工時更可貼上抗爭標語的貼紙在身上,搭車時可讓更多人看到加入。我主張是和平, 成本細, 可長久抗爭, 可令更多人認同的方式......"},{"pid":"ef447df6a21a6f300dc9dd7ff7b9fdb5610dc986","tid":1289597,"uid":274862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"因為成本細才可以長遠推行, 遊行就照做, 目的是希望更多中間派加入!"},{"pid":"88e2a3df5dda11627a9e167e9ddff9b16330c985","tid":1289597,"uid":257020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:20:04.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"d83ebd061e881ec24dd6ad888d0077433cf89052","tid":1289597,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b33d28e24a4bac5d2c3ce926a11232e14506a66","tid":1289597,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c669b88748d50030594070d935b9a3759fe89857","tid":1289597,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:36:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"176aaa675cb21b906de9f4c1b2f7af0824e0800b","tid":1289597,"uid":37396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"唔明有乜用，同念力抗共有乜分別<br />\n林鄭得鬼閒理你"},{"pid":"1255adbca1fffe81b1a50e578b3c4991d22c4882","tid":1289597,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"屌你 又話成個7月係黑衫日<br />\nE家又變星期5<br />\n你玩野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid